data.description: Custom Built Home, Contemporary with Southern Coastal Charm, located in popular Monticello Woods Williamsburg. Offering an abundance of living space with a great floor plan with formal dining room, eat in kitchen, front family room, great room and office/study. Great room has built in cabinetry, a fireplace, vaulted ceilings and ceiling to floor windows opening to a deck. Hardwood floors through out most of the 1st floor. 1st floor primary suite is both elegant and spacious. All the bedrooms are a good size, adding to the functionality of this home. Wrap around porch trex decking and is another great area for entertainment and enjoyment. Side load double car garage has access to a finished room in the basement. Custom plantation shutters throughout.
